2016-03-18 08:43:11', '1', '9', 'https://github.com/buyao/learngit/tree/master/ife_task/task_2_1_1', null, null, '2'), ('491', 'Bug', '买明', '2016-03-23 14:08:39', '1', '9', 'https://github.com/kingcos/TeamBug/tree/master/task/task02', 'http://maimieng.com/skipsrc/task02', 'task02 对 task01 进行了略微修改，使得可以更好的使用 CSS，并学习了 DIV+CSS 布局设计。<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPS：感谢您的 Review 及建议，我们将会虚心学习。<br />\r\n代码及 Demo 展示区：http://maimieng.com/2016/programming/ife/<br />\r\nby Team Bug', '2'), ('492', '四川大学1队', '周丹', '2016-03-24 13:50:04', '1', '9', 'https://github.com/scuife/scufe/blob/gh-pages/task2/task2.html', 'http://scuife.github.io/scufe/task2/task2.html', '完整实现了界面的布局和样式', '2'), ('493', '海贼兄弟', '孟浩', '2016-03-25 14:47:57', '1', '9', 'https://github.com/soulclearm/Learn_front_end/blob/dev/public/task2.html', 'http://behappy.leanapp.cn/task2.html', '求大家给review', '2'), ('494', 'js高手之路', '倪振胜', '2016-03-29 15:43:03', '1', '9', 'https://github.com/jshacker007/ife2016/tree/master/stage1/task2', 'http://jshacker007.github.io/ife2016/stage1/task2/index.html', null, '2'), ('495', '东北财经大学网络学院', '孟浩', '2016-03-15 21:19:52', '8', '8.75', 'https://github.com/menhal/menhal.github.io/blob/master/tasks/stage1/task2/group/index.html', 'http://menhal.github.io/tasks/stage1/task2/group/', null, '2'), ('496', '阡陌前端小组', '解旭东', '2016-03-17 22:13:10', '3', '8.67', 'https://github.com/zitonglu/ife.baidu.com/tree/11d6fb3c215e852590d1c00d0bdc44712ee88661', 'http://www.paipk.com/ife/index.html', '一直在修改', '2'), ('497', '床', '周全', '2016-03-15 03:42:41', '2', '8.5', 'https://github.com/team-bed/task2/blob/master/index.html', 'http://htmlpreview.github.io/?https://github.com/team-bed/task2/blob/master/index.html', '任务二', '2'), ('498', '三文鱼', '吴强', '2016-03-19 20:53:42', '2', '8.5', 'https://github.com/sanwenJohnny/ife/blob/gh-pages/task002/task002.html', 'http://sanwenjohnny.github.io/ife/task002/task002.html', null, '2'), ('499', '红鲤鱼与绿鲤鱼与驴队', '袁广鑫', '2016-03-17 20:54:44', '4', '9.25', 'https://github.com/yuanguangxin/Baidu_ife/tree/master/mission1_3', 'http://yuanguangxin.github.io/Baidu_ife/mission1_3/index.html', '按要求完成了Demo,团队介绍未完待续~~', '3'), ('500', 'TURING', '崔小林', '2016-03-15 09:47:07', '1', '9', 'https://github.com/Front-TURING/BaiDu-IFE/tree/master/Lin/The-First-Stage/task3', 'http://htmlpreview.github.com/?https://github.com/Front-TURING/BaiDu-IFE/blob/master/Lin/The-First-Stage/task3/index.html', '三列布局选用了双飞翼模式，欢迎各位review，用力吐槽~~', '3'), ('501', 'Happy coding', '李晨星', '2016-03-16 20:06:54', '4', '9', 'https://github.com/andy1li/baidu-ife-2016-spring/tree/master/task-1-3', 'http://andy1li.github.io/baidu-ife-2016-spring/task-1-3/task-3.html', '思路：HTML的顺序为“左右中”；左右边栏分别float到左右，中间栏设置相应的左右margin。', '3'), ('502', '写代码也要按照基本法', '叶国雄', '2016-03-16 23:35:31', '1', '9', 'https://github.com/glenye/ife2016/tree/gh-pages/task3-1', 'http://glenye.github.io/ife2016/task3-1/3.html', '尝试了position和float两种方式<br />\r\n目前浅显的认识是float最好用于布局<br />\r\nposition:absolute可以用于小物件的位置定位', '3'), ('503', 'FE_Coding', '林梓标', '2016-03-17 20:56:21', '2', '9', 'https://github.com/Sunshinelzb/IFE_01_Stages/tree/gh-pages/Task_1_03', 'http://sunshinelzb.github.io/IFE_01_Stages/Task_1_03/', '双飞翼布局，初学者，欢迎指正。', '3'), ('504', 'js高手之路', '倪振胜', '2016-03-29 16:00:16', '2', '9', 'https://github.com/jshacker007/ife2016/tree/master/stage1/task3', 'http://jshacker007.github.io/ife2016/stage1/task3/index.html', '通常简单的做法是在html中采用左栏-右栏-中栏的顺序定义，实现简单。这里保持了html中左栏-中栏-右栏的顺序，实现上使用了margin-right为负值的情况', '3'), ('505', 'IFE最强小队', '张星', '2016-03-21 22:41:13', '4', '8.75', 'https://github.com/refine1017/baidu_ife/tree/master/task3', 'http://refine1017.github.io/baidu_ife/task3/', null, '3'), ('506', '迎风小队', '舒慕蓉', '2016-03-21 14:41:40', '3', '8.67', 'https://github.com/amumustyle/ifebaidu2016/tree/gh-pages/task_1_3', 'http://amumustyle.github.io/ifebaidu2016/task_1_3/task_1_3.html', null, '3'), ('507', '帝都小战队', '李宝英', '2016-03-17 18:44:45', '10', '8.6', 'http://krystalbai.github.io/task1-3/', 'https://github.com/KrystalBai/task1-3', '同时实现了浮动版，绝对定位版与margin负值版', '3'), ('508', '湖工大在线', '杨少波', '2016-03-15 19:19:18', '2', '8.5', 'https://github.com/zj972/zj972.github.com/tree/master/ife/task_1_3', 'http://zj972.github.io/ife/task_1_3/', '快来review！！！/(ㄒoㄒ)/~~', '3'), ('509', '明光村幼小大一班', '韩辉', '2016-03-25 15:26:37', '1', '10', 'https://github.com/BUPTSmallHuoban/BUPTSmallHuoban.github.io/tree/master/task4', 'http://buptsmallhuoban.github.io/task4/', null, '4'), ('510', '火大前端', '余兴良', '2016-03-16 14:21:28', '18', '9.5', 'https://github.com/JerryMark1/mypage2.git', 'http://jerrymark1.github.io/mypage2/%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D%E5%92%8C%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98-position.html', '这些是我只能想到的居中的方法，代码有什么问题，欢迎review', '4'), ('511', '三文鱼', '吴灿丽', '2016-03-19 15:17:57', '7', '9.29', 'https://github.com/cherry037/task4', 'http://cherry037.github.io/task4', '我们这种居中方法是用在元素不定宽高的情况下，随着浏览器窗口的变化，宽高也随之改变。请大家多多点评讨论。', '4'), ('512', '对对队', '张奇琦', '2016-03-16 20:52:14', '2', '9', 'https://github.com/Phoebe-Perry/ife_baidu_2016', 'https://phoebe-perry.github.io/ife_baidu_2016/first_phase/ife-baidu_task_4/task_4.html', null, '4'), ('513', 'FED', '孙彦伟', '2016-03-17 20:23:01', '1', '9', 'https://github.com/sun871785469/task4/tree/gh-pages', 'http://sun871785469.github.io/task4/task1-4.html', '百度前端学院FED团队task1-4', '4'), ('514', '代码狗大队', '李欣', '2016-03-17 22:06:34', '1', '9', 'https://github.com/Great-Li-Xin/baidu-ife/tree/master/task4', 'http://baidu-ife.lixin-computer.com/task4/', 'Look ! Ma I&#039;m coding HTML with CSS !', '4'), ('515', 'IFE.FrontEnd', '陈慕杰', '2016-03-18 13:37:49', '1', '9', 'https://github.com/pcdqc/IFE.FrontEnd/tree/master/TeamIntro/public/task/task-4', 'http://121.42.196.46/task/task-4/', '绝对定位水平垂直居中，相对定位Demo（http://121.42.196.46/task/task-4/index-1.html）', '4'), ('516', 'sunshine FE', '杨光', '2016-03-18 22:52:35', '2', '9', 'https://github.com/aquqriusone/sunshine-FE/tree/master/stage-I', 'http://aquqriusone.github.io/sunshine-FE/stage-I/task4.html', null, '4'), ('517', '前端泡沫组', '巫海维', '2016-03-19 2